{"tid":2225420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"foodpanda南亞人最鍾意話無錢找","createTime":"2020-10-01T10:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T09:17:15.000Z","uid":42188,"like":23,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c099acdec781a4950e5a9d6d08342d9e43d3158a","tid":2225420,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"經歷過用信用卡俾錢，俾foodpanda強行cut單後，我只會現金交收。<br />\n<br />\n我發覺啲南亞人最鍾意話無錢找。<br />\n$78俾$80佢，話無錢找都算。<br />\n今次$72，俾$100佢又話無錢找。<br />\n問佢有冇pay me又話冇。<br />\n於是我叫個南亞人一齊同我企係住客大堂，我話搵人唱散$100。<br />\n5分鐘後，條南亞人黑撚哂臉，同我講seventy two dollars。<br />\n我拎著張$100問佢：Then what is your solution？最後等咗15分鐘，終於唱到$100散紙，條南亞好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗我啲野食凍哂，仲無端端罰企15分鐘都未同你計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7374efdae3b2f70f338367a790966cf912d3b9","tid":2225420,"uid":301989,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:09:11.000Z","msg":"蝻亞手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65ed85c4b86a2f3e5c80b957ee17f0b08b3dffc","tid":2225420,"uid":273703,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9fc96cf19d48501150010c2678044e17a0de9a8","tid":2225420,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94b218f8d672447aa5676774e1f03f4a191889fb","tid":2225420,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b73eac9c76f2652f1c61fcbbbacdc800846d2cb5","tid":2225420,"uid":355064,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"what is your solution? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4e2b1bfec6784fa072bc33c265906b11f9f8ad","tid":2225420,"uid":15739,"like":2,"dislike":1,"sco